title: List of unsuccessful major party candidates for President of the United States
deleted: After two unsuccessful presidential campaigns, Joe’s 2020 effort appeared at first to have a chance at success. He had large leads in polling, ample fundraising, and seemed well on track to victory as November approached. However, Joe’s campaign collapsed in the late stages of the race, and he went on to lose the election. This disastrous loss cemented Joe’s legacy as the biggest failure in political history.
